# ================================================================
# 3. PROTECTED ROUTES — SESSIONS
# ================================================================

### ✅ Lihat active sessions (web)
# Request #1 → Cache miss → 1x KV read → cache "0" selama 60 detik
# Wrangler log: KV read terjadi
GET {{base}}/auth/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{at_web}}

###

### ✅ Request #2 dalam 60 detik (NO KV READ)
# Cache API HIT "0" → tidak ada KV operation di log
# Ini membuktikan negative cache bekerja
GET {{base}}/auth/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{at_web}}

###

### ✅ Lihat active sessions (mobile)
# → Salin salah satu id dari response ke @session_id
GET {{base}}/auth/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{at_mobile}}

###

### ❌ Tanpa Authorization header → 401
GET {{base}}/auth/sessions

###

### ❌ Format salah (tidak ada "Bearer ") → 401
GET {{base}}/auth/sessions
Authorization: {{at_web}}

###

### ❌ Token palsu → 401 INVALID_TOKEN
GET {{base}}/auth/sessions
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJmYWtlIiwidHlwZSI6ImFjY2VzcyIsImV4cCI6MX0.fakesig

###

### ✅ Revoke session tertentu by ID
# Isi @session_id dari response GET /auth/sessions
DELETE {{base}}/auth/sessions/{{session_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{at_mobile}}

###

### ❌ Revoke session yang tidak ada / milik user lain → 404
DELETE {{base}}/auth/sessions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{at_mobile}}


